      "How partial inventory scenarios work — e.g., customer wants 5 units but only 3 are available at checkout",
      "Whether the 15-minute timeout resets on customer activity or is a hard deadline from checkout initiation",
      "What constitutes a valid refund reason or whether all refund requests within the window are automatically accepted",
      "Whether listed products with zero inventory should show an out-of-stock indicator or appear identical to in-stock products"
